---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base 
 title="iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly: Which is Best for You? (2026)" 
 description="We compared the three giants of online English learning. Find out which platform fits your goals, budget, and schedule."
>
 <Header />
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pt-6">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">›</span>
      <a href="/compare/" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Comparisons</a>
      <span class="mx-2">›</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-400">iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly</span>
    </nav>
  </div>
 <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
 <div class="mb-12 text-center">
 <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Comparison Guide</span>
 <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-4 mb-6 text-gray-900">iTalki vs Preply vs Cambly: Which is Best for You?</h1>
 <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We compared the three giants of online English learning. Find out which platform fits your goals, budget, and schedule.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
 <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">iTalki</h3>
 <p class="text-emerald-400 font-bold text-lg mb-4">9.2/10</p>
 <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-sm">The world's largest tutor marketplace. Best for flexibility and niche languages.</p>
 <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li>Pay per lesson</li>
 <li> 30,000+ tutors</li>
 <li>No monthly fees</li>
 </ul>
 <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Preply</h3>
 <p class="text-emerald-400 font-bold text-lg mb-4">8.5/10</p>
 <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-sm">Structured learning with a subscription model. Best for consistent progress.</p>
 <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li>Subscription based</li>
 <li>Structured plans</li>
 <li>Great search filters</li>
 </ul>
 <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Cambly</h3>
 <p class="text-emerald-400 font-bold text-lg mb-4">8.0/10</p>
 <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-sm">Instant access to native speakers. Best for conversational practice anytime.</p>
 <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2 mb-8">
 <li>Instant lessons</li>
 <li> 100% Native speakers</li>
 <li>Casual environment</li>
 </ul>
 <a href="/reviews/cambly/" class="block text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Read Review</a>
 </div>
 </div>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6">Pricing Comparison</h2>
 <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Pricing is often the biggest factor for students. Here is how they stack up:</p>
 <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
 <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
 <thead>
 <tr class="bg-slate-800/40">
 <th class="p-4 border-b">Feature</th>
 <th class="p-4 border-b">iTalki</th>
 <th class="p-4 border-b">Preply</th>
 <th class="p-4 border-b">Cambly</th>
 </tr>
 </thead>
 <tbody>
 <tr>
 <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Min. Price</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">$5/hour</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">$10/hour</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">$15/hour</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Payment Type</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">Pay per lesson</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">Subscription</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">Subscription</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 <td class="p-4 border-b font-semibold">Trials</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">Discounted trials</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">100% satisfaction guarantee</td>
 <td class="p-4 border-b">Paid 15-min trial</td>
 </tr>
 </tbody>
 </table>
 </div>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6">Which One Should You Choose?</h2>
 <div class="space-y-8">
 <div>
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose iTalki if...</h3>
 <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">You want total control over your spending. iTalki is the only platform here that does not force you into a subscription. It is perfect if you have a busy schedule or a tight budget.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose Preply if...</h3>
 <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">You want to build a long-term habit. The subscription model keeps you accountable. Preply is also excellent if you need a tutor for a specific professional goal, like passing the IELTS or preparing for a job interview.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Choose Cambly if...</h3>
 <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">You just want to talk. Cambly is great for learners who are shy and want to practice conversation in a low-pressure environment. You can log in at any time and find a tutor ready to chat.</p>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="mt-16 bg-blue-900/40 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-blue-100">
 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Verdict</h2>
 <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">For most learners, iTalki remains the top choice due to its flexibility and massive selection of tutors. However, if you prefer a structured learning path, Preply is a very close second.</p>
 <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
 <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Start with iTalki</a>
 <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="bg-white text-blue-400 border border-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-900/40 transition-colors">Compare Preply</a>
 </div>
 </div>
    <!-- See Guru CTA -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/40 to-indigo-900/40 border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Try See Guru — 3 Free Lessons, No Card Required</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Skip the hunt. Get matched with a certified English tutor and start speaking today. No subscription, no credit card, no strings attached.</p>
      <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-500/30 transition-all">
        Start My Free Lesson →
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-emerald-200/70 mt-4">Trusted by 50,000+ English learners worldwide.</p>
    </div>

 
    <aside class="mt-12 mb-4 p-6 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Related comparisons</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
        <li><a href="/compare/cambly-vs-see-guru/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">Cambly vs See Guru</a></li>
        <li><a href="/compare/see-guru-vs-cambly/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">See Guru vs Cambly</a></li>
        <li><a href="/compare/see-guru-vs-italki/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">See Guru vs Italki</a></li>
        <li><a href="/compare/see-guru-vs-preply/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">See Guru vs Preply</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-slate-700 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Want to skip the comparison and just try the option we recommend? <a href="/reviews/see-guru/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">See Guru</a> gives you 3 free lessons with certified teachers, no card required.
      </p>
    </aside>

  </article>

